national missile defense system which intercepted and destroyed an
unarmed missile on a 25,600-kph collision course over the Pacific.
</P>
<P>
An unarmed missile lifted off from Vandenberg Air Force Base in
California. A "kill vehicle", which lifted off from the Kwajalein
test range in the South Pacific about 21 minutes later,
intercepted and collided with the target above the ocean. (US-
Missile)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
