this level of reserves is 415.4 million dollars less than one
month before. (Colombia-Foreign Reserves)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
NEW DELHI -- India's inflation rate remained static at 2.02
percent for the week ending September 18, despite a marginal
increase in overall Wholesale Price index (WPI).
</P>
<P>
According to the Reserve Bank of India, during the week, annual
rate of inflation remained unchanged at 2.02 percent compared to 8.
61 percent in the corresponding last year. (India-Inflation)
